<HEAD>
<TITLE>
Power Reactor Information System - PRIS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER>
<H2>Nuclear Power Reactors
<BR>
The PRIS Database</H2>
<P>
<HR>
<I>
PRIS - Power Reactor Information System - is an IAEA on-line database covering the world's nuclear power plants. Presented here is an overview of the system, plus selected graphs and data about global nuclear power development. </I>
<HR>
</CENTER>
<P>
<DL>
<P>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF="whatispris.html">What is PRIS</A>
<P>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF="reactors.html">Anniversary of Reactors (Table)</A>
<P>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF="/worldatom/inforesource/pressrelease/prtable.html">Nuclear Power Reactors in Operation and Under Construction at the End of 1995 (Table)</A>
<P>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
