<DOCHDR>
http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/programs/sg/pia3813.htm 193.81.60.210 19970114181254 text/html 3081
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 14 Jan 1997 18:12:29 GMT
