<HEAD>
<TITLE>
OSART
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<H2>
HOW IS AN OSART CARRIED OUT?
</H2>
<P>
<H3>
Sequence of events
</H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>
Missions consist of four stages:
<P>
<UL>
<LI>
Preparing for an OSART.
<LI>
Carrying out the review. 
<LI>
Following up after the mission.
<LI>
Reporting results to the industry.
</UL>
<P>
<hr size=3>
