<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
OSART
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<H2>
HOW IS AN OSART CARRIED OUT?
</H2>
<P>
<H3>
Following up after the mission
</H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>
Approximately one year to eighteen months after the OSART
mission,
a Follow-up visit is conducted.  During this visit, a group of
three to four team members evaluate the progress made in
resolving
the issues raised by the OSART team by interviewing personnel,
reviewing documentation and conducting field visits.  The status
of
the response to each recommendation and suggestion is determined,
and is included in the final report.
<P>
<hr size=3>
<P>
<CENTER>
<A HREF=seven.html><IMG SRC=/worldatom/inforesource/other/gallery/button_n.gif
border=0
align=right></A>
<A HREF=five.html><IMG SRC=/worldatom/inforesource/other/gallery/button_p.gif
border=0
align=left></A>
<A HREF=index.html><IMG SRC=/worldatom/inforesource/other/gallery/button_m.gif
border=0
align=center></A>
</CENTER>
<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<P>
