for text and multimedia presentations.  Knowledge of Hypertext Markup
Language (HTML), FTP, Telnet, and such conversion/graphics
applications as Adobe Photoshop, Acrobat, Illustration, Freehand or
Corel Draw.  Some editorial work experience.
