<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>	Nuclear Engineer</TITLE></HEAD><BODY bgcolor=#ffffff><center><font color=#545454><b>
<i>Applications are invited from suitably qualified women as well as men</I></B></font></center>
<HR NOSHADE><center><FONT SIZE=+2>Nuclear Engineer<BR> Vacancy Notice No.:96/079</FONT><BR><strong>Grade:</strong>	P-4
<HR NOSHADE><strong>Organizational Unit</strong><br>	Nuclear Fuel Cycle and Materials Section
	Division of Nuclear Power and the Fuel Cycle
<BR></CENTER><P><UL><LI><B>Date:</B>10 October 1996<LI><B>Closing Date:</B>	10 February 1997    
<LI><B>Reporting Date:</B>	as soon as possible	
