<HEAD>
<TITLE>Vacancy Notice No.:	96/074	
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff>
<center>
<font color=#545454>
<b><i>Applications are invited from suitably qualified women as well as men</I></B>
</font>
</center>
<HR NOSHADE>
<center>
<FONT SIZE=+2>	Documentation Specialist
</FONT>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+2>Vacancy Notice No.:	96/074	
</FONT>
<BR>
<strong>Grade:</strong>	P-4
<HR NOSHADE>
<strong>Organizational Unit</strong>
<br>
Section of Instrumentation Development - Division of Development and Technical Support - Department of Safeguards
<BR>
</CENTER>
<P>
<UL>
<LI><B>Date:</B>	3 September 1996
<LI><B>Closing Date:</B>	3 January 1997
